<tip category="Rosegarden|General">
<html>
<p>...that can select your autosave interval from Settings->Configure
Rosegarden?
</html>
</tip>
<tip category="Rosegarden|General">
<html>
<p>...that you can create a default studio by copying any .rg or .rgd file to
~/.kde/share/apps/rosegarden/autoload.rg?
</html>
</tip>
<tip category="Rosegarden|General">
<html>
<p>...that Rosegarden can detect and create a default connection for ALSA soft
synths that are started after Rosegarden is already running?</html>
