<tip category="Rosegarden|General">
<html>
<p>...that if you misplace a note, you can move it one halfstep at a time with the up
and down arrow keys on your keyboard.
</html>
</tip>
<tip category="Rosegarden|General">
<html>
<p>...that you can toggle stem directions in the notation editor by selecting
one or more notes and using ctrl-PgUp and ctrl-PgDwn?
</html>
